<div class="container" id="sections">

    <div class="row">

        <div class="col-md-4 col-md-push-8">
            <div id="section-head">
                <h2>About</h2>
            </div>
            <div id="intro">
                <p>
                    <strong>Economics</strong> is a pathbreaking journal that adopts an open
                    source approach to publication, viewing research as a cooperative
                    enterprise between authors, editors, referees, and readers. It is
                    one of only very few Open-Access Journals in Economics with an impact
                    factor.
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li><i class="ai ai-open-access"></i>
                    Free Open Access Publishing</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-university" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    200+ prestigous Co-Editors</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-comments" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                        Open and fast Peer-review</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-bar-chart" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    Strong Data Availability Policy</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Editor: Dennis Snower</p>
                <div id="intro-logos">
                    <ul>
                        <li><img id="ifwlogo" src="++theme++zbw.ejDiazo/static/img/logo.ifw.en.bw.trans.invert.png" /></li>
                        <li><img id="zbwlogo" src="++theme++zbw.ejDiazo/static/img/zbw-logo-trans-invert.png" /></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

